channel.title: How can I add this thing
channel.description: I want to switch my silab gameframe to the 474 gameframe with the hp thing and log out thing in the right corner, and like the new text area but I don't know how, anyone know?

item.title: How can I add this thing
item.dc:creator: @The_Reaper_X The Reaper X
item.description:
@The_Reaper_X wrote:

You need to turn the class files into java files. You’re going to need a decompiler for that i suppose, but considering i haven’t seen anyone actually do it, i don’t think you’ll do it.

search ‘jad’ on google, and a decompiler should be your first result.
